<i>noun</i>: 정부 [정부], 애호가 [애ː호가], 애인 [애ː인] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>정부 [정부]</dt><br>
<dd>lover</dd><br>
<dd>남편이 아니면서 성관계를 하고 깊이 사귀는 남자.</dd><br>
<dd>A man who is not married to a woman but is in a serious and sexual relationship with her.</dd><br>
<dt>애호가 [애ː호가]</dt><br>
<dd>lover; fan; enthusiast</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사물이나 일을 사랑하고 좋아하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who loves a certain object or work and is devoted to it.</dd><br>
<dt>애인 [애ː인]</dt><br>
<dd>lover; one's beloved</dd><br>
<dd>남녀 간의 사랑하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who loves or is loved in a romantic relationship between a man and woman.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>